.TH "calipso_tlv_len" 9 "calipso_tlv_len" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
calipso_tlv_len \- Returns the length of the TLV
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" calipso_tlv_len
.BI "(struct ipv6_opt_hdr *opt "  ","
.BI "unsigned int offset "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "opt" 12
the option header
.IP "offset" 12
offset of the TLV within the header
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the length of the TLV option at offset \fIoffset\fP within
the option header \fIopt\fP.  Checks that the entire TLV fits inside
the option header, returns a negative value if this is not the case.
